    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Objects made of brick, particularly those having a design or image impressed, carved, or painted upon them. For brick used in construction and having a purpose basically utilitarian rather than decorative, prefer "brick (clay material)."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
